    "raw_ingredients": "ISOPROPYL PALMITATE • ETHYLHEXYL PALMITATE • ALCOHOL DENAT. • DIISOPROPYL SEBACATE • BIS-ETHYLHEXYLOXYPHENOL METHOXYPHENYL TRIAZINE • ETHYLHEXYL TRIAZONE • BUTYL METHOXYDIBENZOYLMETHANE • C12-15 ALKYL BENZOATE • DICAPRYLYL CARBONATE • ETHYLENEDIAMINE/STEARYL DIMER DILINOLEATE COPOLYMER • SQUALANE • DROMETRIZOLE TRISILOXANE • PENTAERYTHRITYL TETRA-DI-T-BUTYL HYDROXYHYDROCINNAMATE • TOCOPHEROL • PARFUM / FRAGRANCE (F.I.L. N70038708/1).",
